com.djrapitops.plugin.command

Class ColorScheme

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.djrapitops.plugin.command.ColorScheme

  • public class ColorScheme
extends Object
    Class that contains ChatColors for plugins.

    Colors should be defined in MineCraft format, eg. "§1" "§a" "§o§3"

    Since:
    2.0.0
    Author:
    Rsl1122
